    I hope im not messing anything up, I had 500 emails to go through.

    Megatron turned to Aracnia, and metioned, "This cloning business is 
rather tricky....and could be used agianst us. I really dont trust her in 
charge of them. What if she kills us and uses them to lead our troops?" He 
siad, in a mean stiff tone.
    Aracnia shiged, "Just because thats something you would do dosent mean 
thats what Kitkat is going to do. Paranoia is going to break us apart if you 
dont stop."
    He turned away. This was getting very, very bizzar. Standing up, he 
exited the room and headed for the bridge. At least there he could see how 
Kitkat command her troops....and point out her flaws.
